OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK inflation rate drops to 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F6.8% as energy costs ease  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, UK inflation slowed in July due to     
OL,6, falls in the price for gas and         
OL,7, electricity, official figures show.    
OL,9,FInflation, which measures how prices   
OL,10,Fchange over time, fell to 6.8% in the  
OL,11,Fyear to July, down from 7.9% in June.  
OL,13,FA reduction was expected by analysts,  
OL,14,Fand there are signs the cost of living 
OL,15,Fcould be easing, after figures on      
OL,16,FTuesday revealed wages rose 7.8%       
OL,17,Fannually between April and June.       
OL,19,FBut prices remain high, putting        
OL,20,Fpressure on household finances.        
